data.description: Welcome to this Kingwood hidden gem! Darling first story condominium with views of the pond and clubhouse. This spacious one-bedroom condominium boasts high ceilings, large windows, and tile and carpeted floors throughout. Newly renovated by the owner, this modern unit is one of a kind. This bright, 1-bedroom condominium offers an oversized walk in closet as well as a covered patio to enjoy evenings on. Kingwood Village Estates is a 55+ community that offers a peaceful setting in a friendly environment, that's in the heart of Kingwood. Residents have social activities, pool, spa, club house and exercise room offered for their enjoyment. Instead of renting, this is a perfect and affordable place to invest in and call your own!
